  "prompt": "Which is the best website for booking cheap air tickets?",
  "response": "There are several websites known for offering competitive prices on flight tickets:\n\n1. Skyscanner\n- Compares prices across multiple airlines\n- Flexible search options\n- Often finds good deals\n\n2. Kayak\n- Comprehensive search engine\n- Price forecasts\n- Allows price alerts\n\n3. Google Flights\n- User-friendly interface\n- Price tracking\n- Explore destinations feature\n\n4. Momondo\n- Searches multiple travel sites\n- Often finds lower prices\n- Price calendar view\n\n5. Expedia\n- Can bundle flights with hotels\n- Offers reward points\n- Wide range of options\n\n6. Kiwi.com\n- Unique route combinations\n- Flexible ticket searches\n- Sometimes cheaper than traditional booking\n\n7. Momondo\n- Compares prices across multiple sites\n- Price calendar\n- Good for international flights\n\nEach website has strengths, so it's recommended to compare prices across multiple platforms. Also, booking directly with airlines can sometimes offer better deals or more flexibility.\n\nRemember that prices can vary depending on date, destination, and current promotions.",
